---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---

<Layout title="Nos Services | Jour de Chance" description="L'agence média agile pour transformer les Startups en Scale-ups. Offline & Online.">
  <Header />

  <section class="bg-slate-50 py-24 border-b border-gray-100">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 text-center">
      <span class="inline-block py-1 px-3 rounded-full bg-teal-100 text-teal-700 text-xs font-bold tracking-wide uppercase mb-6">
        Nos Expertises
      </span>
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-extrabold text-gray-900 mb-6 leading-tight">
        Tous les leviers de croissance<br>
        <span class="text-teal-500">activables en 48h.</span>
      </h1>
      <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mx-auto">
        Ne choisissez plus entre la puissance de la TV et la précision du Digital.
        Nous orchestrons vos campagnes sur tous les canaux.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-20">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4">
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
         
         <a href="/solutions/tv-ctv" class="group bg-white p-8 rounded-3xl shadow-sm hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-300 border border-gray-100 hover:border-teal-200 relative overflow-hidden flex flex-col">
            <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-indigo-50 text-indigo-600 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center text-3xl mb-6 group-hover:scale-110 transition">📺</div>
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3 group-hover:text-indigo-600 transition">TV & CTV</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 mb-6 flex-grow text-sm leading-relaxed">
              Accédez au mass média (TF1, M6) et à la TV Connectée. Brand Lift & Drive-to-Web inclus.
            </p>
            <span class="text-indigo-600 font-bold flex items-center gap-2 text-sm">Découvrir l'offre <span class="group-hover:translate-x-1 transition">→</span></span>
         </a>

         <a href="/solutions/ooh-dooh" class="group bg-white p-8 rounded-3xl shadow-sm hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-300 border border-gray-100 hover:border-pink-200 relative overflow-hidden flex flex-col">
            <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-pink-50 text-pink-600 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center text-3xl mb-6 group-hover:scale-110 transition">🏙️</div>
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3 group-hover:text-pink-600 transition">Affichage (DOOH)</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 mb-6 flex-grow text-sm leading-relaxed">
              Visibilité urbaine, Gares et Métros. Ciblage "Sniper" basé sur la localisation GPS.
            </p>
            <span class="text-pink-600 font-bold flex items-center gap-2 text-sm">Découvrir l'offre <span class="group-hover:translate-x-1 transition">→</span></span>
         </a>

         <a href="/solutions/social-vol" class="group bg-white p-8 rounded-3xl shadow-sm hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-300 border border-gray-100 hover:border-blue-200 relative overflow-hidden flex flex-col">
            <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-blue-50 text-blue-600 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center text-3xl mb-6 group-hover:scale-110 transition">📱</div>
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3 group-hover:text-blue-600 transition">Social Ads & VOL</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 mb-6 flex-grow text-sm leading-relaxed">
              TikTok, Insta, YouTube. Des packs "Growth" incluant Création + Média pour baisser votre CAC.
            </p>
            <span class="text-blue-600 font-bold flex items-center gap-2 text-sm">Découvrir l'offre <span class="group-hover:translate-x-1 transition">→</span></span>
         </a>

         <a href="/solutions/search-seo" class="group bg-white p-8 rounded-3xl shadow-sm hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-300 border border-gray-100 hover:border-orange-200 relative overflow-hidden flex flex-col">
            <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-orange-50 text-orange-600 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center text-3xl mb-6 group-hover:scale-110 transition">🔍</div>
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3 group-hover:text-orange-600 transition">Search & SEO</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 mb-6 flex-grow text-sm leading-relaxed">
              Google Ads et Référencement Local. Soyez le premier résultat quand on vous cherche.
            </p>
            <span class="text-orange-600 font-bold flex items-center gap-2 text-sm">Découvrir l'offre <span class="group-hover:translate-x-1 transition">→</span></span>
         </a>

         <a href="/solutions/radio-audio" class="group bg-white p-8 rounded-3xl shadow-sm hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-300 border border-gray-100 hover:border-teal-200 relative overflow-hidden flex flex-col">
            <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-teal-50 text-teal-600 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center text-3xl mb-6 group-hover:scale-110 transition">📻</div>
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3 group-hover:text-teal-600 transition">Radio & Audio</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 mb-6 flex-grow text-sm leading-relaxed">
              Podcasts et Radio hertzienne. Entrez dans l'intimité de vos prospects par la voix.
            </p>
            <span class="text-teal-600 font-bold flex items-center gap-2 text-sm">Découvrir l'offre <span class="group-hover:translate-x-1 transition">→</span></span>
         </a>

         <a href="/contact" class="group bg-gray-900 p-8 rounded-3xl shadow-sm hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-300 border border-gray-900 flex flex-col justify-center items-center text-center">
            <span class="text-5xl mb-6 group-hover:scale-110 transition">🚀</span>
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-2">Autre levier ?</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-400 mb-6 text-sm">
              Nous faisons du sur-mesure. Discutons de votre besoin.
            </p>
            <span class="inline-block px-6 py-2 bg-white text-gray-900 rounded-full font-bold text-sm hover:bg-teal-500 hover:text-white transition-colors">
                Contactez-nous
            </span>
         </a>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <Footer />
</Layout>
